column3: â€œSPIRIT LIFTER. Although dealing with major depression this week and fighting suicide ideation, this brought my spirits up. â€œI'm no Tommy Chong, but I've had a fair share of herb in my lifetime, and this is absolutely the strongest strain I have EVER had.  Supposedly tested at a whopping 30% THC, I was so euphoric I couldn't talk much for the first hour, which is a rare thing for me, indeed.

â€œEasily one of my favorite strains. Despite being an indica and having the #1 effect be sleepiness, I find this to be a very controllable high.
